ture\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ἰ͡ε\u003C/span>ναρίων ἡμ̣[έρ]ᾳ Σε[λ] \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ήνης ἐτελεύτησεν \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐάγριος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐάγριος\">Εὐάγριος\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ἐτῶν ἴκοσι´ ἡμε[ρῶν \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.4 reg., orig. ἴκοσι\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[..]ΟΟΚΤΩΚΑΛΑΝΔΩΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ι͡Ε\u003C/span>ΝΑΡΙΩΝΗ.[..]ΑΣΕ[.]\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΗΝΗΣΕΤΕΛΕΥΤΗΣΕΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐάγριος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐάγριος\">ΕΥΑΓΡΙΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΕΤΩΝΙΚΟΣΙΗΜΕ[...\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.4 reg., orig. ἴκοσι\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001072_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001072_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001072.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001072-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text after Kaibel, compared against Paci\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"1\">1: ΚΑΛΑΝΔΕΙΝ\u003Cspan>Bergk, ap. Kaibel from the stone\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"2\">2: [Φ]ε[βρ]αρίων\u003Cspan>Paci\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"3\">3: ΗΛ...Α\u003Cspan>Bergk, ap. Kaibel, from the stone, for ἡμ[έρ]α\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"4\">4: ϹΥΝΛΡΙΟϹΜΑΛΙΚΟϹΙΗΜΕ\u003Cspan>Bergk, ap. Kaibel from the stone; reading here is that proposed by Kirchhoff (Kaibel \"vix vera sunt\"), followed by Paci\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The text is preserved only in a manuscript tradition, and readings, particularly of the final line, depend upon conjectural interpretation of the letters originally recorded by Schubart.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 54.0928 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Bergk 1843 675 no. V \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002465\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002465\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kirchhoff 1877 9523 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249\" target=